To verify reproducibility of the core findings, we reran the main experiment 10 times for selected CAV shares (those used in Fig. 3). We obtained statistical significance of the results presented in Fig. 2 (with \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$p<0.001$$\end{document}) using the paired two-tailed t-test with nine degrees of freedom, see Appendix.
